      "rationale": "At MRL 2, software quality assurance requires documented version control and basic regression testing. ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 is used under a validated commercial solver qualification plan. Version control is maintained in the project repository with SHA-tagged solver binaries. Regression test suite (15 benchmark cases) passed with no regressions.",
