      "rationale": "Code verification at MRL 2 requires demonstration that the solver correctly implements the governing equations. The Navier-Stokes solver was verified against three analytical benchmark solutions (Poiseuille flow, lid-driven cavity at Re=400, and Stokes flow past a sphere) with observed order of accuracy within 5% of theoretical second-order convergence rate.",
